    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You absolutely have to see this beauty. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
