    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example is mechanically flawless, with a comprehensive service history detailing a bulletproofed VANOS system and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The high-revving naturally aspirated engine breathes through factory individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via the variable M differential lock. The exterior retains its original deep luster, while the interior features supple Nappa leather with no bolster wear. Zero deferred maintenance, no bushing deflection, and a factory-spec suspension geometry make this a definitive driver's car for the discerning collector.",
